name: Dystopian and authoritarian world
description:
There are undercover cops on every corner and hunting illegal immigrants. but there is no racist system here, you have to perform tasks as dangerous as russian roulette to get a visa. Those who do not dare to enter them flee and hunt begins

I was afraid to enter to the competition and my flatmate she had a visa but very badly traumatised because of her past task.

And I had a daschund like AI dog with me who transform to different shapes and its name was Kiki lol
then I entered to a school building because there were a hidden room for the injured survivors

then the police stormed the building and killed everyone, then I noticed (I think) that there are trackers on my clothes and I jumped to a river (at center of the city like european cities) then I was nude and running in the streets. Then it became a routine this chase between police and me

Then I found the turkish ambassy but the turkey was communist in this realm haha but after the revolution they had nearly nothing and they couldn’t help me. I just wanted a new Turkish ID card because I lost them during the police storm
Finally they give me a towel and I talked with a strange old fortune taller lady. Then I figured out she was a healer

by @burkabayramart
